OL,3,CBumper pay rise proposal for MLAs: The
OL,4,Creasons for 30% increase
OL,6,FStormont's 90 MLAs could receive a
OL,7,Fbumper #14,000 pay rise under new
OL,8,Fproposals.
OL,10,FThe Independent Remuneration Board,
OL,11,Fthe panel that sets their salaries,
OL,12,Fhas made the recommendation, comparing
OL,13,Fsalaries with elected representatives
OL,14,Faround the UK and Ireland.
OL,16,FJustifying the increase the board said
OL,17,Fit reflected the requirements of the
OL,18,Fjob, saying no one should be put off
OL,19,Fstanding for election based on the
OL,20,Fsalary. the board stressed it was
OL,21,Findependent of MLAs.
