OL,3,CBumper pay rise proposal for MLAs: The
OL,4,Creasons for 30% increase
OL,6,FMLAs currently earn #53,000 a year,
OL,7,Fwith the new 28.6% pay boost raising
OL,8,Ftheir annual salary to #67,200.
OL,10,FIn addition to the proposed salary
OL,11,Fhike, the board acknowledged public
OL,12,Fdissatisfaction with Northern
OL,13,FIreland's "stop-start government".
OL,15,FThey noted that heavy financial
OL,16,Fpenalties would be enforced if an
OL,17,FExecutive fails to form after future
OL,18,Felections, or if the positions of
OL,19,Ffirst Minister and deputy first
OL,20,Fminister are left unoccupied.
