OL,3,CBumper pay rise proposal for MLAs: The
OL,4,Creasons for 30% increase
OL,6,FMLAs, the Assembly Commission and the
OL,7,FAssembly Members' Pension Trustees,
OL,8,Fwill now submit feedback on the
OL,9,Fadjustment as part of a two-week
OL,10,Fconsultation before a final
OL,11,Fdetermination at the beginning of
OL,12,FMarch.
OL,14,FAlan Lowry, chairperson of the board
OL,15,Fsaid: "The board's objectives are to
OL,16,Fprovide MLAs with a level of
OL,17,Fremuneration which fairly reflects the
OL,18,Fcomplexity and importance of their
OL,19,Fwork and does not deter anyone from
OL,20,Fseeking election on financial grounds.
