OL,3,CBumper pay rise proposal for MLAs: The
OL,4,Creasons for 30% increase
OL,6,F"Our MLAs are elected to demanding
OL,7,Froles which they perform within their
OL,8,Fown constituencies and at Parliament
OL,9,FBuildings.
OL,11,F"They make important decisions around
OL,12,Flegislation, holding ministers and
OL,13,Fdepartments to account and their work
OL,14,Fon the Assembly's scrutiny committees.
OL,16,F"It is important this work, as well as
OL,17,Frepresenting the views and concerns of
OL,18,Ftheir constituents, is recognised and
OL,19,Fvalued.
