OL,3,CBumper pay rise proposal for MLAs: The
OL,4,Creasons for 30% increase
OL,6,F"It is not appropriate, or fair, to
OL,7,Fexpect MLAs to set their own salaries
OL,8,Fand the board operates completely
OL,9,Findependently of the Assembly and the
OL,10,FAssembly Commission.
OL,12,F"We want to ensure that public money
OL,13,Fis spent with probity, accountability,
OL,14,Fvalue for money and transparency. We
OL,15,Fhave made this draft determination
OL,16,Fhaving regard to the current financial
OL,17,Fcircumstances in Northern Ireland."
